  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
      St Stephen Tech Bridge is a community initiative founded in loving memory of Stephen Riak. We equip African youth with essential digital, mathematical, and communication skills needed for success in higher education and beyond.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="programs">
    <h2>Programs</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Basic Computer Skills:</strong> Typing, MS Office, email, internet use</li>
      <li><strong>Functional English:</strong> Grammar, writing, public speaking</li>
      <li><strong>Foundational Math:</strong> Arithmetic, percentages, problem-solving</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Duration: 6-week training bootcamp | Certification Provided</p>
  </section>

  <section id="impact">
    <h2>Our Impact</h2>
    <p>
      Through our pilot cycle, we aim to empower over 50 students with certified skills to boost academic and career opportunities, especially in rural communities.
    </p>
  </section>

